@Node Description "Description"

  Description
  ===========

   This door is crucial to HydraBBS, it waits for incoming calls
   and answers them.

   It does this:

   * Display "Await" special screen, or display internal screen if the "Await"
     screen is present.

   * Call external doors according to function key presses.

       (Currently it does not call any doors itself, the Node programs
       calls the "AccountEdit" system door).

   * Check for incoming calls
     - sets N_ND->ConnectBaud accordingly.

   * Check for local logins
     - sets N_ND->ConnectBaud to "LOCAL"

   * Check for Node shutdown requests

   * Set N_ND->LoginType correctly

@EndNode


